{"tid":1421161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五四運動 火燒趙家樓 會否喺香港重演？","createTime":"2019-08-06T07:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T10:40:57.000Z","uid":293677,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"013a47aa693b7170642394e89c03ab18ab36eab2","tid":1421161,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:12:20.000Z","msg":"火燒趙家樓<br />\n<br />\n五四運動期間，學生因北洋政府的巴黎和會代表談判不力，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>把矛頭對準3名代表，稱之為賣國賊</strong></span>，包括當時的財政總長兼交通總長、被視為親日派的曹汝霖，並在<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">遊行示威期間燒毀了曹汝霖的住宅趙家樓</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港民眾憤怒之火已經點燃，而且越燒越旺。<br />\n火燒趙家樓 會否喺香港重演？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n朱門酒肉臭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：反對一切 不合理的 暴力行為"},{"pid":"e5b5fb4f7869ef79aa3eae58ff00ab35f93d8cad","tid":1421161,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:13:54.000Z","msg":"紅燒狗肉 只是個開端?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be36906a767988bafa9f79657eeebe0bd45a39f","tid":1421161,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:08.000Z","msg":"自推 一次"},{"pid":"2ca60c98e7e0a9baa6fdd4df185626be9fd263b5","tid":1421161,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:20.000Z","msg":"自推 兩次"},{"pid":"8cfc53a110fa576e6addda260ca20b9e9223448e","tid":1421161,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T07:17:33.000Z","msg":"自推三次"},{"pid":"61bedb7a85dd536bc214bca1a1c347457b32fd35","tid":1421161,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:02:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b79ce9b23b023b9ff6c85f17fff68123614f1c","tid":1421161,"uid":25264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T10:03:20.000Z","msg":"火燒何家樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5beeb513bc3764027e4934e71